  "description": "<b>感谢<a href=\"http://tech.huanqiu.com\" target=\"_blank\">环球网科技</a>的投递</b><br /> 众所周知，曾经以Walkman闻名全球的索尼公司是一家消费电子公司，但该公司的主要盈利业务却是金融和娱乐影视。近年来，索尼的消费电子业务损失惨重，直接使得公司持续负债。法新社6月3日报道，对冲基金投资大亨罗布(Daniel&#160;Loeb)建议索尼调整娱乐业务，推动该业务15%-20%的股份公开上市，使管理层腾出手来，把重点放在带领消费电子业务走出困境上。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2cc136ad/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239682.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%B9%E5%86%B2%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%A8%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E5%88%86%E6%8B%86+%E4%BB%A5%E9%87%8D%E6%8C%AF%E6%B6%88%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239682.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%B9%E5%86%B2%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%A8%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E5%88%86%E6%8B%86+%E4%BB%A5%E9%87%8D%E6%8C%AF%E6%B6%88%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239682.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%B9%E5%86%B2%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%A8%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E5%88%86%E6%8B%86+%E4%BB%A5%E9%87%8D%E6%8C%AF%E6%B6%88%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%9A%E5%8A%A1\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239682.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%B9%E5%86%B2%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%91%E5%A4%A7%E4%BA%A8%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE%E7%B4%A2%E5%B0%BC%E5%88%86%E6%8B%86+%E4%BB%A5%E9%87%8D%E6%8C%AF%E6%B6%88%E8%B4%B9%E7%94%B5%E5%AD%90%E4%B8%9A%E5%