  "description": "<b>根据Kantar调查公司针对美国24万智能手机用户进行的调查后发现在二三四这三个月之间Android占据了全美智能手机出货量的51.7%，而苹果 位居第二，占据了41.4%，微软位居第三，占据了5.6%。</b>从下面的数据显示尽管Android的出货量相比较去年增长了1.4，但是iOS和WP系统 的增长速度更加迅猛，分别达到了2.3和1.8。<img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2cc13570/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239681.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DKantar%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%AA%E8%87%B3%E5%9B%9B%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%BDAndroid%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%8D%A0%E5%85%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%8451.7%25\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239681.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DKantar%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%AA%E8%87%B3%E5%9B%9B%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%BDAndroid%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%8D%A0%E5%85%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%8451.7%25\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239681.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DKantar%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%AA%E8%87%B3%E5%9B%9B%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%BDAndroid%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%8D%A0%E5%85%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%8451.7%25\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F239681.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5DKantar%EF%BC%9A%E6%88%AA%E8%87%B3%E5%9B%9B%E6%9C%88%E4%BB%BDAndroid%E8%AE%BE%E5%A4%87%E5%8D%A0%E5%85%A8%E7%BE%8E%E5%87%BA%E8%B4%A7%E9%87%8F%E7%9A%8451.7%25\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u